JOHANNESBURG, South Africa, August 30, 2018/APO Group/ --
                                                        
                            National Assembly Speaker, Ms Baleka Mbete, is scheduled to attend a healing prayer service to be held at the University of Johannesburg, Soweto Campus, on Thursday - 31 August 2018.





Ms Mbete will deliver a keynote address at the Service, which is aimed at supporting and motivating students, particularly female students, and assisting them with basic needs.



The details of the event are as follows:



Date: 31 August 2018

Time: 10am

Venue: Imbizo Hall, University of Johannesburg, Soweto Campus